The antibody of claim 16 or claim 17, wherein the anti-angiogenic agent is an antagonist of vascular endothelial cell growth factor (VEGF), optionally an anti-VEGF antibody, further optionally bevacizumab.








The anti-EphB4 antibody of any of claims 1-6, for use in a method of treating a cancer, a tumor, and/or a cell proliferative disorder.








