EphB4 nucleic acid and amino acid sequences are known in the art. Nucleic acid sequence encoding the EphB4 can be designed using the amino acid sequence of the desired region of EphB4. Alternatively, the cDNA sequence (or fragments thereof) of GenBank Accession Nos. NM_004444, or disclosed in 

